ALL - Albanian Lek

The Albanian Lek is the currency of Albania. Our currency rankings show that the most popular Albanian Lek exchange rate is the ALL to USD rate. The currency code for Leke is ALL , and the currency symbol is L. Below, you'll find Albanian Lek rates and a currency converter.
